name: Diamond - Stingray
description:
Stingray - 4th of 10 art from the "Diamond Animals" collection.
Stingrays are one of the most ancient creatures on the planet. Data on the first rays refer to the Lower Jurassic period (about 150 million years ago). Despite the fact that the stingray is a peaceful fish, they have survived most dangerous predators and natural disasters. But now their population is noticeably decreasing due to human interference in the realities of their habitat.
